  "instructions": [
    "Heat a pot over medium heat and pour in the vegetable broth.",
    "Add the tamarind pulp, soy sauce, pickled cucumber juice, and chili flakes; stir until the mixture simmers.",
    "Insert the sliced ginger and galangal, letting them infuse for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the young green jackfruit pieces and mushrooms; cook until the jackfruit turns soft and the broth thickens to a glassy-jelly consistency, about 12 minutes.",
    "Stir in the coconut milk and lime juice, adjusting the heat to keep the broth at a gentle simmer for 3 minutes.",
    "Taste and add more soy sauce or lime juice if acidity is needed.",
    "Ladle the soup into bowls and garnish with fresh cilantro leaves.",
    "Serve hot, accompanied by steamed jasmine rice if desired."
  ],
